Sentencas: Co-firing of a La0.8Sr0.2MnO3-delta(LSM)-gadolinium doped ceria(GDC)/GDC/NiO-GDC cell is investigated by the application of a mixed GDC powder.
Titulo: Co-firing of LSM-GDC/GDC/NiO-GDC with addition of nano-GDC powder

Sentencas: A fine starting GDC powder is synthesized by the homogeneous precipitation process, using hexamethylenetetramine (HMT), and mixed with a commercially available GDC powder.
Titulo: Co-firing of LSM-GDC/GDC/NiO-GDC with addition of nano-GDC powder

Sentencas: Shrinkage behavior of the chemically prepared, the commercial, and the mixed GDC powders is examined by thermo-mechanical analysis (TMA), which suggests that the mixed powder has good sinterability and compatible shrinkage with electrodes.
Titulo: Co-firing of LSM-GDC/GDC/NiO-GDC with addition of nano-GDC powder

Sentencas: A LSM-GDC/GDC/NiO-GDC cell prepared by lamination of electrode and electrolyte green sheets is co-fired at 1300 degrees C for 4 h. The prepared fuel cell gives an output power density of 0.35 W/cm(2) at 600 degrees C. (C) 2008
Titulo: Co-firing of LSM-GDC/GDC/NiO-GDC with addition of nano-GDC powder
